All classes within the MinecraftMediaLibrary.

CompletableFuture classes within the MinecraftMediaLibrary (used for mainly testing, should not be used by the user yet)

Dependency management classes relating to installation, relocation, and loading into the global classpath can be found here.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.dependency.task
Task building utilities.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.dependency.vlc
VLC specific dependency handling can be found here.

A list of exceptions which can be thrown throughout the library.

com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.http
HTTP handling classes including daemons, request handlers can be located here.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.image
Library functions support image processing which allow maps to be painted a specific image.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.listener
A set of listeners used by the library to unregister/register players.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.logger
A built in logger function for MinecraftMediaLibrary only itself to avoid console spam and also allow better debugging details.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.nms
A set of NMS classes used to send and display map packets to users.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.reflection
Package which contains useful Reflection utilities as well as a mini packet listener to substitute for ProtocolLib.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.relocation  
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.resourcepack
A set of resourcepack wrapper utilities and checks to wrap a resourcepack very easily.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.resourcepack.hosting
HTTP daemon providers and other custom resourcepack hosting can be found here.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.test.coolstuff  
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.utility
A set of utility classes used throughout the MinecraftMediaLibrary framework.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.video.dither
Perhaps some of the greatest dithering algorithms which are very performant.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.video.dither.development
Algorithms currently in development.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.video.dither.frame
Algorithms related to frame analysis in a video.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.video.itemframe
Item frame callbacks can be found here, which control the visuals of an item frame.
com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.video.player
A set of build in video players for easier video media controlling.
